author: Brian Johnson
title: Doran starts work on Depot Renaissance Hotel makeover
text:
Home / News / Construction & Development / Doran starts work on Depot Renaissance Hotel makeover Doran Construction has started work on the $12 million Depot Renaissance Hotel renovation in downtown Minneapolis. (Submitted rendering: Doran) Doran starts work on Depot Renaissance Hotel makeover By: Brian Johnson August 18, 2015 5:33 pm 0 Crews will add a fourth floor to the building, and demolish an indoor water park to make room for 110 additional guest rooms, a fitness center, and a pool.
